  "text": ". By applying the method proposed by Wu and Lim with N = 3, the value 1.2352721/A (percentage error, 1.44%) for the approximate frequency is obtained [CITATION_1] . Using this method and N → ∞, the value 1.237330/A (percentage error, 1.28%) is obtained [CITATION_2] .",
